        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Reference contractions were recorded (15 s) while the participant was seated, using the follow- ing positions: trapezius—arms held at 90° abduc- tion in the coronal plane, elbows straight, forearm pronated, holding 1 kg weight; anterior deltoid— arms held at 90° shoulder flexion, forearms pronated, elbows straight holding 1 kg weight.",
        "bbox": [
