        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Four 30 s samples of kinematic data were collected at 0, 5, 10 and 15 min into the keyboard task. Data was filtered at 80 HZ, a sampling rate of 31 samples/s was used, with an averaging constant of 500 ms.",
